---

<section id="experience" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <p class="section-number">Experience</p>
      <h2>Currently building AI systems in production.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 max-w-[700px]">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="mb-0.5">AI Application Engineer</h3>
        <p class="text-[13px] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Full-Time &middot; June 2023 – Present</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="exp-items">
        <li>
          <span class="exp-dot"></span>
          <span><strong>AI Agents & Chat Ecosystems:</strong> Design, develop, and deploy intelligent AI agents and conversational applications tailored to solve complex user needs.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="exp-dot"></span>
          <span><strong>Infrastructure Automation:</strong> Architected and developed Zabbix automation tools to streamline system monitoring, alerting, and operational efficiency.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="exp-dot"></span>
          <span><strong>Full-Stack Implementation:</strong> Build and maintain the end-to-end architecture required to support high-performance AI models in production.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
        <span class="tag">Go</span>
        <span class="tag">Python</span>
        <span class="tag">AI Agents</span>
        <span class="tag">Zabbix</span>
        <span class="tag">Full-Stack</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .exp-items {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .exp-items li {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .exp-items strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .exp-dot {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary);
    margin-top: 0.5em;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    background: var(--canvas-soft);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  }
</style>
